title: Mia Archeep
overview: "Plan" is an Agency for raising perfect wives under the direction of Mr. Robert. Chollada-a girl from a middle-class family who became the best of the students in the "Plan". Mr. Robert believes that Collada will be the perfect wife for Kasidit, and trying to reduce them. Seeing everything as an exciting game, Kasidit agrees, not expecting to fall in love with Chollada for real. He is not sure of Chollada's feelings for him. What is it: love or an elaborate game of "Plan"?
